ximation of forces inside\na cell, an integral approximation of the gravitational and magnetic fields, and\ntensor artificial viscosity that permits an accurate investigation of the\nformation and evolution of shocks in the neutral fluid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2004 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2004 20:55:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
