 we compare in detail with results from chemical-probe experiment.\nMaybe the most central result is that first for clusters with $N$ above 80\ngeneral trends can be identified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Oct 2004 15:13:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-08"}
